Make sure you dowload the Motor Shield Library https://github.com/adafruit/Adafruit-Motor-Shield-library
LCD libary comes standard with the arduino program

Items Used:
Arduino UNO
Arduino Motor Shield
12V Stepper Motor
Breadboard
Several jumper cables and wire
LCD Display
220 and 10K ohm resistors
2 LEDs
2x6-pin and 2x8pin female pin
38 Khz IR receiver
IR remote control
Breadboard-friendly 2.1mm DC barrel jack
12 VDC 1000mA regulated switching power adapter
Photo cell
TMP36 Analog Temperature Sensor
Reel to attach to motor (we 3D printed with the Makerbot)
String to attach to reel
